  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK99">
<l>iṉco liṉitīṉṟal kāṇpā ṉevaṉkolō</l>
<l>vaṉcol vaḻaṅku vatu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who sees what sweet it is that sweet words bring—why, pray!</l>
<l>would he use harsh words?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
